oji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T09:22:30.000Z","msg":"其實呢個官真心幾公正<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"691a5f9ee3731cb9d157cc61cc3ed2345549491b","tid":2374432,"uid":1988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T09:23:42.000Z","msg":"痴撚線 宜家d 低級官個個鬥紅鬥奶<br />\n堵路要還押"},{"pid":"2c886777e45f6d9cf8f20eeacbbb1052d25ef5ab","tid":2374432,"uid":136994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4af141bfeeba85ba1d10a21daff9f60aa1100ae5","tid":2374432,"uid":146351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"70f2ff350083206425afe14361c25abe74bad050","tid":2374432,"uid":110043,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T08:32:11.000Z","msg":"竟然肯攞社會服務令報告咁好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T09:22:30.000Z","msg":"其實呢個官真心幾公正<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T09:28:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e36b8049a2404a43d8225934a55bc929635a0316","tid":2374432,"uid":1988,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4af141bfeeba85ba1d10a21daff9f60aa1100ae5","tid":2374432,"uid":146351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"70f2ff350083206425afe14361c25abe74bad050","tid":2374432,"uid":110043,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T08:32:11.000Z","msg":"竟然肯攞社會服務令報告咁好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T09:22:30.000Z","msg":"其實呢個官真心幾公正<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T09:29:53.000Z","msg":"呢個官嘅history<br />\n－社署女服務員街頭叫罵「黑警」 非法集結拒捕等罪成囚10星期<br />\n－青年涉拒捕辯方質疑總督察證供與新聞片段不符 官指批評不切實際一度拍枱拂袖而去<br />\n－兩男藏雷射筆罪成候判<br />\n－無手令搜屋檢雷射筆 青年藏武器罪成判更生中心<br />\n－警稱遭珍珠奶茶杯掟傷額頭 屯門公園衞生關注組召集人認襲警囚三周<br />\n－男生涉縱火被捕 警無手令上門檢雷射筆改控武器罪 官指警有權搜屋裁定罪成還柙"},{"pid":"84f2473e55f0eabd84d1525a3cd737587ae74bfb","tid":2374432,"uid":146351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2c886777e45f6d9cf8f20eeacbbb1052d25ef5ab","tid":2374432,"uid":136994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4af141bfeeba85ba1d10a21daff9f60aa1100ae5","tid":2374432,"uid":146351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"70f2ff350083206425afe14361c25abe74bad050","tid":2374432,"uid":110043,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T08:32:11.000Z","msg":"竟然肯攞社會服務令報告咁好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T09:22:30.000Z","msg":"其實呢個官真心幾公正<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T09:28:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T09:32:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7f201acf6b6714cb88ec2822b4e7c70c150ccf4","tid":2374432,"uid":39710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T09:34:33.000Z","msg":"唉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />希望唔駛坐"},{"pid":"a77bb1d2faa8f37100d4a7451cc014c68efac5c3","tid":2374432,"uid":55162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"63c6ec8bdefeb98a8ce4fbdda1de091e2c815be7","tid":2374432,"uid":1988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T09:21:36.000Z","msg":"在公眾地方造成阻礙罪 唔告 <br />\n要告非法集結<br />\n<br />\n罪1 2000蚊<br />\n依家就扮晒嘢還押逼人坐監"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T09:39:00.000Z","msg":"諗唔明點解有手足係告阻街<br />\n有d告非法集結<br />\n完全唔明點界定"},{"pid":"de3d1fa38561bb0bfc59af657861b64f6a1111c4","tid":2374432,"uid":92448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T09:41:09.000Z","msg":"黑警+狗官+太監=港共曱甴集團"},{"pid":"9be2d4f40a2cd5616d09ad942e88eb9eaa6b0e67","tid":2374432,"uid":136994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a77bb1d2faa8f37100d4a7451cc014c68efac5c3","tid":2374432,"uid":55162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"63c6ec8bdefeb98a8ce4fbdda1de091e2c815be7","tid":2374432,"uid":1988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T09:21:36.000Z","msg":"在公眾地方造成阻礙罪 唔告 <br />\n要告非法集結<br />\n<br />\n罪1 2000蚊<br />\n依家就扮晒嘢還押逼人坐監"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T09:39:00.000Z","msg":"諗唔明點解有手足係告阻街<br />\n有d告非法集結<br />\n完全唔明點界定"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T09:41:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"771ed44749c9d52e825cc3ecfc6edbaa393b5206","tid":2374432,"uid":1988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a77bb1d2faa8f37100d4a7451cc014c68efac5c3","tid":2374432,"uid":55162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"63c6ec8bdefeb98a8ce4fbdda1de091e2c815be7","tid":2374432,"uid":1988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T09:21:36.000Z","msg":"在公眾地方造成阻礙罪 唔告 <br />\n要告非法集結<br />\n<br />\n罪1 2000蚊<br />\n依家就扮晒嘢還押逼人坐監"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T09:39:00.000Z","msg":"諗唔明點解有手足係告阻街<br />\n有d告非法集結<br />\n完全唔明點界定"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T09:42:47.000Z","msg":"無人知<br />\n不過而家律政司開始將堵路case用非法集結告<br />\n連逼d車要轉線都可以講到意圖令司機乘客受驚 -&gt; 意圖破壞社會安寧<br />\n<br />\n一個就輕鬆坐<br />\n一個就2000鬆人<br />\n<br />\n所以話doj 冇一個人係無辜<br />\n冇一個人"},{"pid":"7744066482e4a881e393c1b5090d0a6680b66e3b","tid":2374432,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T09:42:51.000Z","msg":"去年初疫情來襲，市民為抗議政府拒絕全面封關，遂於多區堵路。天水圍有人向馬路掟單車及垃圾桶，兩名青年被拘控，願承認在公眾地方造成阻礙罪，惟控方堅持控以參與非法集結罪，經審訊後兩人今被裁定罪成。辯方要求只索取社會服務令報告作判刑考慮，惟裁判官王證瑜指「點解唔可以攞埋禁閉式院舍報告先」，下令還柙兩被告，等候索取多份報告再判刑。<br />\n<br />\n王官裁決指控方證人供詞互相脗合，證人亦目睹有被告向馬路擲單車，後來車輛需慢駛及繞過障礙物方能駛去，故接納控方證據，認為被告必然有意圖令在場人士，或相當可能導致任何人合理地害怕如此集結的人會破壞社會安寧，或害怕他們會藉以上的行為激使其他人破壞社會安寧，裁定二人罪成。<br />\n<br />\n首被告大律師一度要求只索取社會服務令報告，惟遭王官多番反問「點解唔可以攞埋禁閉式院舍報告先」，最終下令為兩人索取多份報告包括更生、勞教、教導所及社會服務令報告，不排除判處監禁式刑罰，案件押後至2月5日判刑。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210121/ZCFCQI3EVFC6JMOWPLPPZ46SOM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210121%2FZCFCQI3EVFC6JMOWPLPPZ46SOM%2F&d=PT6dGXJ5JuBAxmbDRmxpcPY%2F4yEwT0EAZMYNsJUacQ0%3D&h=8ff0a148\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210121%2FZCFCQI3EVFC6JMOWPLPPZ46SOM%2F&h=4d91b28e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210121/ZCFCQI3EVFC6JMOWPLPPZ46SOM/</a>"},{"pid":"fa283e7d7baed02dd9e811200e964f7bf23614ff","tid":2374432,"uid":309192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T09:42:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />歷史有日終會證明你地無罪"},{"pid":"e641700491a984a8208cd909730b72754829a121","tid":2374432,"uid":121197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"70f2ff350083206425afe14361c25abe74bad050","tid":2374432,"uid":110043,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T08:32:11.000Z","msg":"竟然肯攞社會服務令報告咁好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T09:43:56.000Z","msg":"攞報告唔代表會判<br />\n有啲Case上到區院擺到明判幾年都會循例拎下社會服務令報告"},{"pid":"23f6a90681ce6fc8e48d1546b991faf8fb3703b4","tid":2374432,"uid":1988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9be2d4f40a2cd5616d09ad942e88eb9eaa6b0e67","tid":2374432,"uid":136994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a77bb1d2faa8f37100d4a7451cc014c68efac5c3","tid":2374432,"uid":55162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"63c6ec8bdefeb98a8ce4fbdda1de091e2c815be7","tid":2374432,"uid":1988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T09:21:36.000Z","msg":"在公眾地方造成阻礙罪 唔告 <br />\n要告